trans-unit.source: The SearchResponse class is sent by the server as a response to a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SearchResponse sendes på serveren som svar på en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This response contains zero or more <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntry"></xref> objects, and zero or more <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Dette svaret inneholder null eller flere <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntry"> </xref> objekter, og null eller flere <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The Controls property contains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref> object returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Kontroller inneholder den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"> </xref> objektet som ble returnert av serveren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref> object returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"> </xref> objektet som ble returnert av serveren.

trans-unit.source: The Entries property contains a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntryCollection"></xref> object that contains the entries returned by the search.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen som inneholder en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntryCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder poster som returneres av søket.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntryCollection"></xref> object that contains the entries returned by the search.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultEntryCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder poster som returneres av søket.

trans-unit.source: The ErrorMessage property contains the error message, if any, for this operation.
trans-unit.target: ErrorMessage-egenskapen inneholder feilmeldingen, for denne operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The error message, if any, for this operation.
The MatchedDN property contains the matched distinguished name returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen MatchedDN inneholder samsvarer unikt navn som er returnert av serveren.

trans-unit.source: The matched distinguished name returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Samsvarer, unikt navn som returneres av serveren.

trans-unit.source: The References property contains a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection"></xref> object that contains search references returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen referanser inneholder en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder Søk referanser returnert av serveren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection"></xref> object that contains search references returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder Søk referanser returnert av serveren.

trans-unit.source: The Referral property contains the server referrals.
The ResultCode property contains a value of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode"></xref> that specifies the result code for the operation.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ResultCode inneholder verdien <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode"> </xref> som angir Resultatkode for operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The result code for the operation.
